Analysis - Class in <Unnamed>
This superclass keeps track of the basic information that an analysis of waste water dischargess must have: The name of the industry that discharged the waste water to a receiving body. The name of the laboratory that took the sample of water and performed the tests to determine the concentration of each pollutant. A 4 character number which serves the laboratory to identify the sample of waste water that was analyzed The date when the sample of waste water was obtained.

Builds an Analysis object with no pollution or compliance results.
